Jacob CORNET, Appellant, v. Tighe E. WOODS, Housing Expediter, Appellee. No. 12341. United States Court of Appeals Ninth Circuit. March 14, 1950. Wexler & Wexler, Millbrae, Cal., for appellant. Ed Dupree, Gen., Counsel, OHE, A. M. Edwards, Jr., Acting Asst. Gen. Counsel, Francis X. Riley and William A. Moran, Sp. Lit. Attorneys, Washington, D. C., for appellee.

Before MATHEWS and BONE, Gircuit Judges, and MATHES, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment of the District Court is affirmed.
